Benin – The Presidential candidate of the Labour Party in the last Presidential election, Peter Obi, received a rousing welcome in Benin city, Edo state today March 11 as he visited the state for his party’s governorship campaign. Youths in the state were so excited they used their shirts to clean his car as he made his way to the campaign ground. Watch videos that captured the moment below… A post shared by Lindaikejiblog (@lindaikejiblogofficial)